OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny start for most places,
OL,6,Fwith any early mist quickly clearing.
OL,7,FCloud then spreads across the region,
OL,8,Fbut it will remain dry, bright and
OL,9,Fwarm or very warm. Breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight
OL,12,Fwith patchy light rain in the north
OL,13,Fand some occasional breaks in the
OL,14,Fcloud. Winds easing but breezy along
OL,15,Fthe coasts. Temperatures mild
OL,16,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
